{
 "name": "RPlog_Prize_Awards_Shooting_Contest",
 "title": "Prize Awards Shooting Contest",
 "summary": "At the Half Moon Hotel and Casino on Bonadan, a high-profile marksmanship contest sponsored by Merr-Sonn draws a glittering, dangerous crowd of competitors and spectators. Bounty hunters, Imperial officers, and assorted scoundrels -- among them Boba Fett, Athena, Cernious, Paro, the officer Sargent, Kizuka, Scaven, and many others -- mingle amid the neon and gambling machines, eyeing the prize tables of fine weapons and gadgets. The event blends shooting competition with the intrigue, posturing, and quiet deal-making of the galaxy's underworld and military elite gathered in one glamorous casino.",
